# üõí Sales Dashboard ‚Äì Supermarket Shop

An interactive **Sales Dashboard** designed to analyze supermarket performance using **Power BI**.  
The dashboard provides insights into **sales, profit, product performance, categories, payment modes**, and **time-based trends**.

---

## üìä Dashboard Overview

![Sales Dashboard](img/img2.png)  
![Sales Data](img/img1.png)  
![Sales Dashboard View](img/img3.png)

---

## üîë Key Metrics

- **Total Sales**
- **Total Profit**
- **Profit Percentage**
- **Top Product**
- **Top Category**

---

## üéõ Filters & Slicers

- **Year** (2021, 2022)
- **Month**
- **Sale Type**
- **Payment Mode**

All visuals update dynamically based on slicer selections.

---

## üìà Visualizations Included

- Monthly **Sales & Profit Trend**
- Daily **Sales Trend**
- **Product-wise Sales** (Bar Chart)
- **Category-wise Sales** (Treemap)
- **Sales Type Distribution** (Donut Chart)
- **Payment Mode Distribution** (Donut Chart)

---

## üßÆ DAX Measures Used

### Total Sales
```DAX
Total Sales =
SUM ( 'Sales'[Total Selling Value] )
```

### Total Profit
```DAX
Total Profit =
SUM ( 'Sales'[Profit] )
```

### Profit %
```DAX
Profit % =
DIVIDE ( [Total Profit], [Total Sales], 0 )
```

### Monthly Sales
```DAX
Monthly Sales =
CALCULATE (
    [Total Sales],
    ALLEXCEPT ( 'Date', 'Date'[Month Name], 'Date'[Year] )
)
```

### Daily Sales
```DAX
Daily Sales =
CALCULATE (
    [Total Sales],
    ALLEXCEPT ( 'Date', 'Date'[Day] )
)
```

### Sales by Product
```DAX
Sales by Product =
SUM ( 'Sales'[Total Selling Value] )
```

### Sales by Category
```DAX
Sales by Category =
CALCULATE (
    [Total Sales],
    VALUES ( 'Product'[Category] )
)
```

### Sales by Sale Type
```DAX
Sales by Sale Type =
CALCULATE (
    [Total Sales],
    VALUES ( 'Sales'[Sale Type] )
)
```

### Sales by Payment Mode
```DAX
Sales by Payment Mode =
CALCULATE (
    [Total Sales],
    VALUES ( 'Sales'[Payment Mode] )
)
```

### Top Product (by Sales)
```DAX
Top Product Sales =
MAXX (
    TOPN (
        1,
        VALUES ( 'Product'[Product Name] ),
        [Total Sales],
        DESC
    ),
    [Total Sales]
)
```

### Top Category (by Sales)
```DAX
Top Category Sales =
MAXX (
    TOPN (
        1,
        VALUES ( 'Product'[Category] ),
        [Total Sales],
        DESC
    ),
    [Total Sales]
)
```

---

## üß† DAX Concepts Applied

- SUM  
- CALCULATE  
- DIVIDE  
- VALUES  
- TOPN  
- MAXX  
- ALLEXCEPT  
- Filter Context & Evaluation Context  

